import React from 'react'; import { TableContainer, Table, TableRow, TableCell, Paper, Link } from '@mui/material'; const StockInfoTable = ({ data }) => { return ( Sector {data.sector} Industry {data.industry} Exchange {data.exchange} Country Name {data.country_name} ISIN {data.isin} Primary Ticker {data.primary_ticker} Web URL Link Fiscal Year End {data.fiscal_year_end}
); }; export default StockInfoTable;
